metadata.name: Suns Can Be Black
metadata.description:
Decades ago, a grade school  teacher chastised me when I drew a landscape picture with a black sun. For the longest time I thought I did something wrong, but turns out...Suns can be black...if you want them to be.  

This piece is hand drawn then converted to code art. 

Draw what you want, create what you feel, leave the critics to their popcorn and canap√©s.
